
Prerequisites
==============

the following tools are needed:
   autoconf libtool automake autopoint pkg-config

the following headers are needed:
   libjpeg62-dev libudev-dev libconfig++8-dev libjson0-dev

for initial scan files:
   dvb-apps


Checkout TVDaemon
==================

git clone https://github.com/neolynx/tvdaemon.git
cd tvdaemon

Build tvdaemon
===============

git submodule init
git submodule update

cd v4l-utils
git checkout master
git am ../patches/*
autoreconf -i
./configure
make
cd ..

cd cli-core
git co master
git submodule init
git submodule update
cd src/colorful
git co master
cd ../../..

libtoolize
autoreconf -i
./configure
make

